description:
Lind is a first class goddess of the special duty category, a Valkyrie.
It`s said that she`s the most extreme goddess because of the intense training she went through by herself.
Other names of her are "The Fighting Wing" (戦う翼, Tatakau Tsubasa) and "One-Winged Angel" (片よくな天使, Katayoku na Tenshi). The latter name derives from the fact that her angel has only one wing.
Lind has a third name due to her being special in some way but that`s something you can find out yourself by watching http://anidb.net/a5426 [Aa! Megami-sama: Tatakau Tsubasa].
name: Lind
